# Allowlist of packages that the daw.sdk module is permitted to export.
#
# Format: one fully-qualified package name per line. Blank lines and lines
# starting with `#` are comments.
#
# This file is the *single source of truth* for the daw.sdk public API
# surface. ModuleExportsAllowlistTest fails if module-info.java and this file
# disagree, so adding/removing exports requires a deliberate update here.
#
# See docs/ARCHITECTURE.md > "Module export tiers" for the three-tier model
# (public API / SPI / internal).
